import React from 'react'
import './Home.css';
import { Header , Container} from './section/index'
import { Card , Button} from './components/index';
function Home() {
  return (
    <>
    <Header/>
      <Container>
      <Card image=''
        title='Creative'
        soustitle='"Design creates culture. Culture shapes values. Values determine the future."'
        signature='Robert L. Peters'
      />
       <Card image=''
        title='Innovative'
        soustitle='“There are 360 degrees, so why stick to one?”'
        signature='ZAHA HADID'
      />
       <Card image=''
        title='Qualitative'
        soustitle='"Design creates culture. Culture shapes values. Values determine the future."'
        signature='Robert L. Peters'
      />
      </Container>
      <Button text='Start Your Project'/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Home
